  "_about": "Single Trigger for the discover-project Workflow per ADR-004 (fail-fast on missing entity, no auto-route). v1 ships only the manual Trigger — the founder runs /sulis:discover-project explicitly. The candidate auto-suggest-on-missing-entity Trigger (FR-003) is deferred to v2 until real founder-experience evidence shows fail-fast is too costly; until then the principle of governance over mystification (release-train ADR-001) holds — one command, one effect, no surprise state changes. Tenant ULID is the canonical marketplace tenant; workflow ULID is byte-identical to workflow.jsonld and steps.jsonld.",
