      "description": "Manual entry point — founder-initiated. The only Trigger in v1 per ADR-004 (governance over mystification). When a non-discover-project command needs a Project entity and doesn't find one, it fails-fast with an explicit error telling the founder to run /sulis:discover-project first — no auto-routing. Flags: --update (per ADR-005, activates the per-field diff re-discovery flow); --path <sub-path> (per MUC-007, scope Detect to a sub-directory in a monorepo); --source-repo <org/name> (per MUC-006, override when no git remote is configured).",
